WEBVTT

01:39.300 --> 01:43.190
[Road to Success]

01:44.700 --> 01:47.880
[Episode 23]

01:48.310 --> 01:49.710
You all remember

01:49.710 --> 01:50.840
Robert's Rules of Order

01:50.840 --> 01:52.479
I taught you before, right?

01:52.479 --> 01:53.229
Yes.

01:53.229 --> 01:54.870
You make it sound so mysterious,

01:54.870 --> 01:56.640
but isn't it just
the principle of majority rule?

01:56.640 --> 01:57.789
It seems Qin Ao

01:57.789 --> 01:59.650
listens very carefully in class.

02:00.710 --> 02:03.000
This time,
we are not going with majority rule.

02:03.000 --> 02:04.040
Today,

02:04.560 --> 02:06.200
we are going to take a vote.

02:06.200 --> 02:06.870
A vote?

02:07.400 --> 02:08.310
How?

02:11.080 --> 02:12.540
Regarding the next match,

02:13.150 --> 02:15.080
you haven't reached a conclusion.

02:15.630 --> 02:17.240
Should we forfeit?

02:17.240 --> 02:17.870
Forfeit?

02:17.870 --> 02:19.329
If Wen Chengye isn't here,

02:19.710 --> 02:20.910
are we still playing?

02:21.079 --> 02:23.140
Doesn't that mean we aren't playing?

02:26.710 --> 02:28.240
I will give each of you

02:28.240 --> 02:29.680
a blank piece of paper later.

02:29.680 --> 02:31.030
Those who don't want to play

02:31.030 --> 02:32.520
can draw a cross on it.

02:33.560 --> 02:34.870
If there is even a single cross

02:34.870 --> 02:36.170
among the 10 votes,

02:36.310 --> 02:37.310
we will...

02:38.079 --> 02:38.710
forfeit.

03:19.280 --> 03:20.160
Time's up.

03:21.970 --> 03:22.780
Let's start.

03:52.870 --> 03:54.079
Then I'll begin.

03:56.710 --> 03:57.560
The 1st one.

04:00.280 --> 04:01.080
Blank.

04:09.160 --> 04:09.920
Blank.

04:17.430 --> 04:18.230
Blank.

04:26.240 --> 04:27.000
Blank.

04:35.810 --> 04:36.659
Blank.

04:42.030 --> 04:42.790
Blank.

04:49.000 --> 04:49.790
Blank.

04:55.460 --> 04:56.260
Blank.

05:02.130 --> 05:03.240
The last two votes.

05:13.780 --> 05:14.630
Blank.

05:19.200 --> 05:21.090
I'm having a heart attack.

05:25.010 --> 05:25.960
The last one.

05:30.180 --> 05:31.280
It's the last one.

05:58.240 --> 05:59.040
Blank.

06:06.390 --> 06:07.270
Oh, no.

06:07.270 --> 06:08.780
I kind of want to cry.

06:08.800 --> 06:09.680
Why?

06:10.430 --> 06:11.590
We won't forfeit.

06:11.620 --> 06:13.500
Let's beat the crap out of them.

06:13.520 --> 06:14.400
Yeah.

06:14.430 --> 06:16.290
So what if we only have ten people?

06:16.360 --> 06:17.480
We're going to play!

06:17.480 --> 06:17.940
Yeah!

06:17.970 --> 06:19.040
-Yeah!
-That's right!

06:19.040 --> 06:20.320
-Beat the crap out of them!
-We'll play!

06:20.320 --> 06:21.630
-Yeah!
-No one says 10 people can't play.

06:21.630 --> 06:22.720
As long as we're together,

06:22.720 --> 06:24.160
we can play even with 10 people!

06:24.160 --> 06:26.030
It seems the answer is already obvious.

06:26.030 --> 06:27.400
Not only will we not give up,

06:27.400 --> 06:28.660
but we also can't chicken out!

06:28.660 --> 06:30.080
With such an ace coach,

06:30.100 --> 06:31.390
even with only 10 people,

06:31.390 --> 06:32.150
we can still win!

06:32.150 --> 06:33.390
-Right?
-Yeah.

06:33.390 --> 06:34.470
Coach is here.

06:35.070 --> 06:36.800
You're too optimistic, Qin Ao.

06:37.240 --> 06:39.240
It's okay even if we lose.

06:39.240 --> 06:40.920
We play for fun.

06:40.920 --> 06:41.360
Right!

06:41.360 --> 06:42.950
We'll be happy even if we lose?

06:42.950 --> 06:44.270
If we lose, I'll kick your ass nonstop.

06:44.270 --> 06:45.560
Can you even catch me?

06:45.580 --> 06:46.210
We'll play until we retire!

06:46.210 --> 06:47.030
Play until we retire!

06:47.030 --> 06:47.890
Play until we retire!

06:47.890 --> 06:49.090
Play until we retire!

06:58.280 --> 06:59.210
That's great.

07:00.650 --> 07:02.210
I am proud of you.

07:09.160 --> 07:10.480
[Chen Jianghe, Second Class]
[Lin Lu, Second Class]

07:10.510 --> 07:12.050
[Hongjing to Chuncheng North Station,
D07016]

07:13.980 --> 07:15.380
I've booked the tickets.

07:35.350 --> 07:36.010
Warm water.

07:36.040 --> 07:36.640
Thank you.

07:44.310 --> 07:45.110
What's wrong?

07:46.120 --> 07:48.520
I still don't want to give up
on Wen Chengye.

07:49.210 --> 07:50.409
Wen Chengye right now

07:50.720 --> 07:52.450
is like an injured pufferfish.

07:53.070 --> 07:54.670
Instead of approaching him,

07:54.680 --> 07:55.670
it's better

07:56.120 --> 07:57.780
to let him choose for himself.

08:04.630 --> 08:07.840
[Hello, Wen Chengye]

08:09.270 --> 08:09.750
Pung!

08:10.510 --> 08:11.630
I was so close.

08:12.750 --> 08:13.680
What kind of luck is that?

08:13.680 --> 08:14.360
I'm on fire!

08:16.160 --> 08:19.270
It's all Wang's fault.
He keeps dealing into your hands.

08:19.270 --> 08:20.480
I won't give up today.

08:44.370 --> 08:45.700
[Hengjiu Crushed Hongjing No. 8 High]

09:01.440 --> 09:02.140
[The Opponent Lost Their Composure]

09:02.170 --> 09:03.030
[Yongchuan Hengjiu's Legendary Storyline—
More Thrilling Than a Novel]

09:05.320 --> 09:05.440
[The Opponent Lost Their Composure]

09:05.470 --> 09:05.590
[Yongchuan Hengjiu's Legendary Storyline—
More Thrilling Than a Novel]

09:07.220 --> 09:10.150
[Inbox]

09:08.390 --> 09:09.630
Hello, Wen Chengye.

09:10.150 --> 09:17.250
[Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team's
Fixtures and Related Assignments]

09:10.440 --> 09:12.630
First, according to
the organizing committee,

09:12.630 --> 09:14.440
our next Youth Super League match

09:14.440 --> 09:16.360
is scheduled for next Sunday at 2 p.m.

09:16.360 --> 09:19.030
We will play an away game
against Chuncheng Xinpeng.

09:19.030 --> 09:21.910
The match venue and address
are as follows.

09:23.150 --> 09:25.010
[Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team's
Fixtures and Related Assignments]

09:25.150 --> 09:30.260
[Chuncheng North Station]
[Yongchuan Chuncheng Sports Center]

09:26.080 --> 09:28.550
Second, I assigned

09:28.570 --> 09:29.970
homework to the players.

09:30.040 --> 09:31.160
The topic is:

09:31.240 --> 09:33.080
Football is for Victory.

09:33.670 --> 09:36.070
You can submit your homework
in any format,

09:36.200 --> 09:38.550
such as an essay or a comic.

09:38.200 --> 09:38.990
[Lin Wanxing]

09:39.120 --> 09:41.910
I hope you'll submit it
on time by next Sunday.

09:39.180 --> 09:45.000
[Yongchuan Chuncheng Sports Center]

09:42.720 --> 09:44.910
Third, I'll send you
the match review video

09:44.910 --> 09:46.550
via a cloud drive.

09:46.790 --> 09:47.910
Please download it yourself.

09:47.360 --> 09:53.070
[Lin Wanxing]

09:48.390 --> 09:49.200
P.S.

09:49.510 --> 09:51.120
We will take
the high-speed rail to Chuncheng.

09:51.120 --> 09:52.650
The schedule is as follows.

09:53.200 --> 09:55.550
Swipe your ID card
and you'll find a surprise.

09:55.550 --> 09:57.810
Your beloved teacher, Lin Wanxing.

09:55.710 --> 09:56.370
[Lin Wanxing]

09:56.490 --> 09:57.660
[Hongjing to Chuncheng North Station,
G3001]

09:57.690 --> 09:59.390
[Wen Chengye, Second Class]
[Fu Xinshu, Second Class]

09:59.410 --> 10:00.440
[Qin Ao, Second Class]
[Lin Lu, Second Class]

10:00.460 --> 10:01.590
[Chen Jianghe, Second Class]
[Zheng Feiyang, Second Class]

10:01.620 --> 10:05.210
[Hongjing to Chuncheng North Station,
G3001]

10:04.330 --> 10:05.390
Weirdo.

10:16.790 --> 10:18.390
Now that we are missing Wen Chengye,

10:18.390 --> 10:19.640
our defense is weak,

10:19.670 --> 10:21.800
so someone has to drop back from midfield.

10:21.800 --> 10:23.710
Actually, I can fill this position.

10:23.710 --> 10:25.430
No, you're not tall enough.

10:25.450 --> 10:28.380
You're at too much of a disadvantage
in aerial duels.

10:29.000 --> 10:30.240
Then you can do it.

10:30.400 --> 10:32.250
No, how can Chen do it?

10:32.360 --> 10:32.960
If Chen drops back,

10:32.960 --> 10:34.150
I'll be the only one left up front.

10:34.150 --> 10:34.720
What about our attack?

10:34.720 --> 10:36.250
Yeah, we'd have no forward.

10:36.670 --> 10:37.870
Then can I do it?

10:37.870 --> 10:39.630
I'm pretty good at clearing the ball.

10:39.630 --> 10:40.890
Bro, here's the thing.

10:41.200 --> 10:41.910
You're too soft on defense,

10:41.910 --> 10:43.080
so your defending is weak.

10:43.080 --> 10:44.030
If they get physical with you,

10:44.030 --> 10:44.960
you're done for.

10:45.360 --> 10:46.000
Right?

10:47.040 --> 10:47.710
Coach,

10:47.750 --> 10:49.270
we can't reach an agreement.

10:49.270 --> 10:50.270
What do you think?

10:53.650 --> 10:54.510
What about you?

10:54.980 --> 10:56.010
Fu?

10:56.670 --> 10:57.510
Of course not him.

10:57.510 --> 10:59.150
He's always been our core in midfield.

10:59.150 --> 10:59.650
Yeah.

10:59.870 --> 11:01.600
Although he always plays midfield

11:01.600 --> 11:02.910
and plays it very well,

11:03.670 --> 11:06.030
considering our team's current situation,

11:06.030 --> 11:07.360
he is the most suitable.

11:11.650 --> 11:12.870
We need you

11:13.030 --> 11:15.300
to bring your passing,
long-ball distribution,

11:15.300 --> 11:16.720
and game-reading ability

11:16.720 --> 11:17.750
to the back line.

11:19.910 --> 11:20.550
Understood.

11:20.550 --> 11:23.210
But your foot hasn't completely healed,
right?

11:23.240 --> 11:24.740
My foot is fine now.

11:24.760 --> 11:25.960
Don't worry about me.

11:26.390 --> 11:27.750
If there are no other opinions,

11:27.750 --> 11:28.630
it's decided.

11:28.630 --> 11:29.630
-Okay.
-Let's do it.

11:29.630 --> 11:31.090
-I think it's okay.
-Okay.

11:31.240 --> 11:32.390
There are only 5 days until the match.

11:32.390 --> 11:34.750
You need to get familiar
with the new lineup quickly.

11:34.750 --> 11:36.390
Be careful and stay safe.

11:36.390 --> 11:36.830
-Okay.
-Alright.

11:36.830 --> 11:37.670
Okay, Ms. Lin.

11:37.670 --> 11:38.750
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

11:38.750 --> 11:39.550
Let's begin.

11:39.840 --> 11:40.570
Give it a try.

11:40.670 --> 11:41.550
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

11:41.550 --> 11:42.810
Let's start training.

11:44.910 --> 11:46.200
Slow down.

11:46.200 --> 11:47.030
Why the rush?

11:47.030 --> 11:48.190
I wasn't me.

11:48.600 --> 11:49.440
Let's go.

11:56.670 --> 11:58.400
Nice first touch! Pass it to me.

12:00.130 --> 12:02.570
[Four Days Until the Match]

12:00.590 --> 12:03.140
♪ Who hasn't known
the dark of night and uncertainty? ♪

12:04.420 --> 12:07.500
♪ Stumbling, covered in wounds,
losing direction ♪

12:06.990 --> 12:09.580
[Four Days Until the Match]

12:08.440 --> 12:13.910
♪ Wandering alone,
gaining strength through pain ♪

12:09.710 --> 12:12.300
[Three Days Until the Match]

12:16.730 --> 12:19.590
♪ Riding the wind,
chasing an unknown horizon ♪

12:17.910 --> 12:19.880
[Two Days Until the Match]

12:19.880 --> 12:23.070
[One Days Until the Match]

12:20.800 --> 12:23.990
♪ Looking up,
dreaming side by side of great ideals ♪

12:24.880 --> 12:30.630
♪ The vast world
awaits youth to arrive ♪

12:28.270 --> 12:30.470
Do you think we can really win tomorrow?

12:31.270 --> 12:32.870
Coach said she never predicts

12:32.870 --> 12:34.470
results other than victory.

12:34.720 --> 12:37.200
Doesn't that mean hope is slim?

12:40.110 --> 12:41.240
I really want to win.

12:41.520 --> 12:43.010
If we lose,

12:43.040 --> 12:45.040
this will be our last game.

12:45.060 --> 12:47.730
I know you want the best for the team.

12:48.310 --> 12:49.390
If you don't want to say it,

12:49.390 --> 12:50.920
you must have your reasons.

12:51.440 --> 12:52.960
If you have the chance,

12:53.140 --> 12:54.840
find some time to talk to them.

12:54.840 --> 12:56.030
Of course we will win.

12:56.030 --> 12:56.870
That's right.

12:56.870 --> 12:58.000
We definitely will.

13:01.600 --> 13:02.270
I'm leaving first.

13:02.270 --> 13:03.000
I'll get going.

13:03.000 --> 13:04.270
-Okay.
-Call me when you get there.

13:04.270 --> 13:05.670
-Bye-bye!
-Bye-bye!

13:05.670 --> 13:06.270
This is what I think.

13:06.270 --> 13:07.030
In our defensive third,

13:07.030 --> 13:08.510
if you get the chance,
pass the ball to Fu.

13:08.510 --> 13:10.750
He'll send a long ball forward.

13:10.750 --> 13:13.270
Okay, bye-bye.

13:14.000 --> 13:15.030
I'm telling you,

13:15.270 --> 13:16.390
the two of you as a...

13:16.390 --> 13:17.720
Everyone works so hard.

13:18.440 --> 13:20.150
-I need to do what I should do as well.
-Let's pass the ball to Fu.

13:20.150 --> 13:21.790
He'll send a long ball forward.

13:21.790 --> 13:23.200
Then the ball goes to Jianghe.

13:23.200 --> 13:24.870
Jianghe can pass it to Ao.

13:24.870 --> 13:25.390
Got it?

13:25.390 --> 13:26.120
That's how it will be.

13:26.120 --> 13:26.870
I'll just...

13:26.870 --> 13:27.390
He...

13:27.390 --> 13:28.720
Fu, where are you going?

13:29.030 --> 13:29.600
Fu!

13:56.260 --> 13:57.380
[Hongjing to Chuncheng North Station,
G3001]

13:57.400 --> 13:58.640
[Wen Chengye, Second Class]

14:07.010 --> 14:09.330
[Hongjing to Chuncheng North Station,
G3001]

14:47.120 --> 14:49.580
I know you resent me
for breaking my promise,

14:49.910 --> 14:51.390
and I know you want to know

14:51.390 --> 14:52.510
why I did this.

14:53.670 --> 14:55.090
I refused to tell you

14:55.320 --> 14:56.700
because it's...

14:57.490 --> 14:58.570
too disgusting.

15:02.320 --> 15:06.900
[Seven years ago]

15:10.270 --> 15:12.000
A birthday gift for you.

15:12.500 --> 15:15.160
-Excuse me. Which ward is Li Xiaomei in?
-Hello.

15:17.640 --> 15:19.920
Bed 21. It's in the room down the hall.

15:23.200 --> 15:24.130
Okay, thank you.

15:28.800 --> 15:30.150
Mom, it's my friend's birthday today.

15:30.150 --> 15:31.410
I'm going out for a bit.

15:33.630 --> 15:34.080
Hello?

15:34.910 --> 15:36.330
Is this Guan Minjie?

15:36.360 --> 15:37.270
Yes, this is she.

15:37.270 --> 15:38.470
I'm a police officer.

15:39.290 --> 15:40.720
Your husband got drunk

15:40.720 --> 15:41.870
and assaulted someone on the street.

15:41.870 --> 15:43.940
The victim is now hospitalized
with severe injuries.

15:43.940 --> 15:45.470
His family wants to sue him.

15:45.510 --> 15:46.970
Please come to the police station
immediately

15:46.970 --> 15:49.100
to cooperate with our investigation.

15:49.270 --> 15:50.240
Okay, I see.

15:51.030 --> 15:52.270
Mom, what's wrong?

15:53.200 --> 15:55.440
Your dad beat someone up
and is in the police station again.

15:55.440 --> 15:57.010
We have to go there.

15:57.680 --> 15:59.040
What did you just say?

16:02.080 --> 16:04.080
I have an emergency at home. I have to go.

16:04.080 --> 16:04.820
Thank you.

16:05.030 --> 16:05.600
It's fine.

16:05.600 --> 16:06.240
I'll go get changed first.

16:06.240 --> 16:07.500
You're coming with me.

16:16.550 --> 16:17.810
Have you paid the fine?

16:23.350 --> 16:31.090
[Public Security]

16:24.440 --> 16:25.240
When you get back,

16:25.240 --> 16:26.700
discipline him properly.

16:27.550 --> 16:28.120
Here.

16:29.150 --> 16:30.790
Sign here and you may leave.

16:34.510 --> 16:36.170
Fu Haisheng needs to sign too.

16:42.620 --> 16:43.530
Fu Haisheng.

16:51.200 --> 16:53.120
Sign here and you may leave.

17:00.360 --> 17:01.030
Thank you.

17:01.030 --> 17:01.560
Goodbye.

17:02.600 --> 17:03.200
Let's go.

17:09.109 --> 17:10.920
I just paid a 5,000 fine.

17:11.930 --> 17:13.680
The salary I just received wasn't enough,

17:13.680 --> 17:15.220
so I borrowed some from my mom.

17:15.220 --> 17:16.480
I don't know what to do

17:16.510 --> 17:18.510
with this month's living expenses.

17:21.790 --> 17:22.849
Are you blaming me?

17:23.270 --> 17:24.240
No.

17:24.240 --> 17:25.480
Are you blaming me?

17:26.109 --> 17:27.000
Are you?

17:27.000 --> 17:27.720
-Don't hit Mom!
-Let go of me!

17:27.720 --> 17:28.650
Blaming me, huh?

17:28.790 --> 17:30.590
-I'm not!
-All you do is blame me!

17:30.920 --> 17:31.920
Don't hit Mom!

17:32.070 --> 17:33.070
Get away!

17:34.000 --> 17:35.180
Look at you!

17:35.510 --> 17:37.200
Just looking at you annoys me!

17:37.200 --> 17:37.790
Stop hitting me!

17:37.790 --> 17:39.240
All you do is blame me!

17:39.640 --> 17:40.720
Blaming me, huh?

17:41.030 --> 17:42.630
Blame me one more time and...

17:44.880 --> 17:46.440
-I told you to stop!
-Xinshu!

17:46.440 --> 17:47.680
How dare you hit Mom!

17:53.070 --> 17:53.960
Stop it!

17:55.750 --> 17:56.710
Officer.

17:57.510 --> 17:59.310
This little brat was out of line.

17:59.920 --> 18:01.350
He actually hit me with a brick.

18:01.350 --> 18:03.030
He even hit me one more time in the face.
Look.

18:03.030 --> 18:04.510
He almost blinded me.

18:07.550 --> 18:08.750
You're glaring at me?

18:08.790 --> 18:09.880
Keep glaring and you'll see!

18:09.880 --> 18:11.000
Calm down. Calm down.

18:11.000 --> 18:11.830
Sit.

18:18.110 --> 18:18.880
Officer,

18:18.880 --> 18:20.410
I have a question to ask you.

18:21.000 --> 18:21.590
Go ahead.

18:22.480 --> 18:23.400
Well...

18:25.680 --> 18:26.680
It's just...

18:28.350 --> 18:30.920
Is a violent tendency hereditary?

18:31.200 --> 18:32.310
Why do you ask?

18:33.470 --> 18:34.510
Just now,

18:35.270 --> 18:37.310
when my son hit his dad with a brick,

18:38.030 --> 18:39.550
I saw the look in his eyes.

18:39.550 --> 18:41.550
It was exactly the same as his dad's.

18:41.790 --> 18:42.910
I'm afraid he

18:43.440 --> 18:44.850
will be like his dad.

18:45.640 --> 18:46.790
Well...

18:47.400 --> 18:49.000
Your son was protecting you.

18:49.000 --> 18:51.030
I know, but I'm afraid of...

18:51.680 --> 18:53.350
What if he hits people too

18:53.390 --> 18:54.390
in the future?

18:55.210 --> 18:56.170
Like me?

18:57.590 --> 18:58.400
Brat.

18:59.400 --> 19:00.400
Did you hear that?

19:00.800 --> 19:03.590
Your mom says
you inherited my violent genes.

19:03.740 --> 19:05.140
Are you going to help her?

19:12.210 --> 19:13.230
Alright.

19:13.260 --> 19:14.870
Let's go back first, okay?

19:19.590 --> 19:21.240
Mom, let's go home.

19:44.590 --> 19:45.920
That's the whole story.

19:47.270 --> 19:48.800
That was when I realized,

19:51.070 --> 19:52.550
I might be just like my dad,

19:53.400 --> 19:55.400
a kid with violent tendencies.

19:58.620 --> 20:00.970
Maybe that's the reason my mom

20:02.270 --> 20:04.790
abandoned me after the divorce.

20:08.030 --> 20:08.830
I am really afraid

20:08.830 --> 20:10.070
of turning into someone like my dad.

20:10.070 --> 20:10.790
Really.

20:13.920 --> 20:15.680
That's also why

20:16.350 --> 20:17.160
I've been a people pleaser

20:17.160 --> 20:19.270
in your eyes all these years.

20:27.380 --> 20:28.580
Wen Chengye.

20:30.140 --> 20:32.420
I want you to play football with us

20:32.660 --> 20:33.550
because I feel

20:33.550 --> 20:35.720
I see hope in football.

20:39.010 --> 20:40.170
I believe you do too.

20:50.310 --> 20:52.880
If... if you can forgive me,

20:54.330 --> 20:56.200
I am right outside your door.

21:14.590 --> 21:16.040
[Fu Xinshu]

21:25.470 --> 21:26.050
[I am really afraid of
turning into someone like my dad.]

21:26.070 --> 21:26.540
[That's also why I've been]

21:26.560 --> 21:27.020
[a people pleaser in your eyes
all these years.]

21:27.040 --> 21:27.430
[If you can forgive me,
I am right outside your door.]

21:39.600 --> 21:39.950
[Ms. Lin told us to go to
Yuanyuan Tutoring Class this weekend.]

21:39.970 --> 21:40.780
[Delete]

21:40.810 --> 21:41.700
[Confirm]

21:41.730 --> 21:42.990
[Ms. Lin told us to go to
Yuanyuan Tutoring Class this weekend.]

21:43.020 --> 21:43.760
[Delete]

21:43.780 --> 21:44.430
[Confirm]

21:44.460 --> 21:44.620
[Ms. Lin told us to go to
Yuanyuan Tutoring Class this weekend.]

21:45.870 --> 21:46.260
[You can tell me if you run into
something like this next time.]

21:46.290 --> 21:46.930
[Delete]

21:46.960 --> 21:47.390
[Confirm]

22:00.200 --> 22:01.070
I scheduled a one-on-one

22:01.070 --> 22:02.770
mock interview tutoring session
for you tomorrow.

22:02.770 --> 22:05.630
The materials are on the desk.
Read them carefully.

22:05.660 --> 22:06.450
Wait.

22:07.640 --> 22:08.560
You must go.

22:09.610 --> 22:10.550
I'll go with you.

22:37.110 --> 22:38.110
Morning, Coach!

22:39.400 --> 22:40.030
Morning.

22:42.000 --> 22:43.750
Why aren't your shoes in your bag?

22:43.750 --> 22:45.310
My bag is full of food.

22:45.310 --> 22:46.740
It'd be so dirty to put them together.

22:46.740 --> 22:47.830
You're quite neat.

22:47.830 --> 22:49.110
Coach, we're here.

22:49.110 --> 22:50.000
Morning, Coach.

22:50.000 --> 22:50.590
Morning.

22:52.480 --> 22:53.410
Where's Ms. Lin?

22:54.680 --> 22:56.170
Ms. Lin was afraid you guys
would be hungry,

22:56.170 --> 22:57.680
so she went to buy some food.

22:57.680 --> 22:58.830
Ms. Lin is so nice.

22:58.830 --> 23:00.030
-Coach!
-Ms. Lin is the best.

23:00.030 --> 23:01.000
Coach!

23:01.960 --> 23:02.830
Hurry up!

23:03.680 --> 23:04.240
Morning.

23:05.400 --> 23:06.440
You're here so early?

23:06.440 --> 23:07.720
We still have some time.

23:07.720 --> 23:09.230
Let's sit down and take a rest.

23:09.230 --> 23:10.350
-Okay.
-Okay.

23:10.350 --> 23:11.310
Let's go.

23:11.310 --> 23:12.880
Give me the bag in your left hand.
Come on.

23:12.880 --> 23:15.680
You want to eat food
that smells like stinky shoes?

23:15.680 --> 23:16.510
A mighty tiger...

23:16.510 --> 23:18.640
is savoring the stench of stinky feet.

23:31.830 --> 23:33.030
Why are you dawdling?

23:34.830 --> 23:35.440
Nothing.

23:53.640 --> 23:54.680
The teacher I hired for you this time

23:54.680 --> 23:57.270
is a real admissions officer
from a prestigious university.

23:57.270 --> 23:59.270
You should cherish this opportunity.

23:59.270 --> 23:59.920
Whatever.

24:07.240 --> 24:08.730
Going abroad as I said and

24:08.750 --> 24:12.350
following the path I've arranged for you
is the right thing to do.

24:12.880 --> 24:16.000
Stop thinking about that low-tier team
as soon as possible.

24:16.000 --> 24:16.790
They are not low-tier.

24:16.790 --> 24:18.350
Then what are they?

24:19.160 --> 24:20.820
Look at the people on the team—

24:21.190 --> 24:23.050
complicated family backgrounds

24:23.070 --> 24:25.030
and a father with violent tendencies.

24:25.030 --> 24:26.000
He's so young,

24:26.000 --> 24:27.440
and he also has violent tendencies.

24:27.440 --> 24:28.770
What do you mean by that?

24:31.390 --> 24:33.790
I saw the messages
on your phone yesterday.

24:35.260 --> 24:36.650
Someone named Fu Xinshu

24:36.680 --> 24:38.340
said he owed you an explanation.

24:38.340 --> 24:40.320
He rambled on and on.

24:40.450 --> 24:41.920
How could you look at my phone?

24:41.920 --> 24:42.450
And then?

24:42.460 --> 24:43.460
Nothing.

24:43.490 --> 24:44.970
I deleted all the messages

24:45.030 --> 24:46.510
that tried to mislead you.

24:51.040 --> 24:52.030
What did he say?

25:01.370 --> 25:02.110
Stop the car!

25:03.790 --> 25:07.550
[Dangerous stunt. Do not attempt]

25:04.660 --> 25:05.520
Come back here!

25:09.920 --> 25:10.650
Wen Chengye!

25:11.310 --> 25:12.040
Wen Chengye!

25:12.880 --> 25:13.590
Come back!

25:22.770 --> 25:25.460
[Ticket checking
will stop 5 minutes before departure.]

25:24.400 --> 25:26.510
They are checking tickets soon.
Come back quickly.

25:26.510 --> 25:27.720
Okay, coming.

25:28.510 --> 25:30.030
So which one do you usually choose?

25:30.030 --> 25:32.150
I usually go for Keen Hearing or Fitness.

25:32.150 --> 25:33.880
I never take Deaf.

25:33.880 --> 25:35.350
Ms. Lin said she'll be right here.

25:35.350 --> 25:36.270
Let's go in first.

25:36.270 --> 25:37.680
-Okay.
-Let's go.

25:37.680 --> 25:39.680
-Don't forget your ID cards.
-Okay.

25:54.490 --> 25:56.070
[Warning: Battery depleted.
Your phone will shut down in 30 seconds.]

25:57.350 --> 25:58.000
Qin Ao.

25:58.000 --> 26:00.200
Qin Ao. Do you have a power bank with you?

26:02.330 --> 26:04.060
I don't think I have it today.

26:05.710 --> 26:08.510
Let's deal with it
after we get off the train, okay?

26:16.580 --> 26:19.390
[Ticket checking has closed for the train
to Chuncheng North Station.]

26:16.750 --> 26:19.610
The train from Hongjing to Chuncheng
has departed.

26:19.790 --> 26:22.400
The train from Shenguang North Station

26:22.400 --> 26:24.860
to Yongfu West Station
is departing at 9:30.

26:29.720 --> 26:32.280
[Information Service]

26:32.430 --> 26:34.290
[Automatic Ticketing]

26:35.740 --> 26:36.490
Chuncheng!

26:36.380 --> 26:36.640
[Ticket Vending Machine]

26:36.730 --> 26:39.550
[Departure: Hongjing]
[Destination: Chuncheng North Station]

26:36.790 --> 26:39.640
Please select your arrival station
on the left.

26:39.640 --> 26:41.680
Please select the departure date.

26:39.690 --> 26:40.940
[Departure Date]

26:43.500 --> 26:45.780
[Departure Date]

26:45.870 --> 26:47.660
[No Matching Trains Found]

26:47.690 --> 26:47.960
[Ticket Vending Machine]

26:52.000 --> 26:52.860
Hey, young man.

26:53.440 --> 26:55.190
Are you going to Chuncheng?

26:55.590 --> 26:56.590
If high-speed rail tickets are sold out,

26:56.590 --> 26:59.110
you can check
the long-distance bus station next door.

26:59.110 --> 26:59.750
Over there?

26:59.750 --> 27:00.680
Right next door.

27:01.440 --> 27:01.960
Thank you.

27:01.960 --> 27:02.550
You're welcome.

27:02.290 --> 27:06.150
[Automatic Ticketing]

27:14.070 --> 27:15.160
We've already departed.

27:15.160 --> 27:16.380
Even though you didn't come,

27:16.380 --> 27:17.880
I still want to tell you

27:18.550 --> 27:20.610
that I really want you to play with us.

27:20.820 --> 27:22.100
We will try hard to win.

27:22.550 --> 27:24.030
If you don't come this time,

27:24.030 --> 27:25.630
we'll try to have a next time.

27:28.200 --> 27:29.850
I'm on my way to Chuncheng.

27:29.980 --> 27:31.440
I won't wait for the next time.

27:31.440 --> 27:32.640
I'm coming this time.

27:33.050 --> 27:34.220
We must win.

27:36.680 --> 27:37.840
Where are you?

27:37.860 --> 27:39.110
For this stupid match,

27:39.110 --> 27:40.590
are you giving up your future?

27:40.590 --> 27:42.000
I am giving you a choice now.

27:42.000 --> 27:43.310
Either you get your ass back here now,

27:43.310 --> 27:45.310
or you never come back to this house!

28:17.030 --> 28:18.290
It's almost time to go.

28:20.030 --> 28:21.720
The goal for today's match

28:23.270 --> 28:25.200
is to lose by as little as possible.

28:27.790 --> 28:30.190
On the field, regardless of your position,

28:30.550 --> 28:33.150
you must always remember
to be ready to defend.

28:33.400 --> 28:34.400
Got it, Coach.

28:34.790 --> 28:36.790
We will try our best to hold them off.

28:38.140 --> 28:39.540
Let me ask you a question.

28:40.590 --> 28:41.200
Among the upcoming attacks

28:41.200 --> 28:42.720
we might face,

28:43.480 --> 28:45.340
which one do you most want to stop?

28:58.490 --> 28:59.620
Sorry, Coach.

29:00.790 --> 29:01.680
We don't know.

29:04.880 --> 29:06.080
Think with your heart

29:06.350 --> 29:07.680
and feel it on the field.

29:08.750 --> 29:09.440
Let's go.

29:10.200 --> 29:11.000
Let's go.

29:11.640 --> 29:12.830
-Go for it.
-Okay! Let's go!

29:12.830 --> 29:13.610
-Go for it!
-We've got this!

29:13.610 --> 29:14.790
We've got this!

29:33.240 --> 29:34.510
Here is the match
between Hongjing No. 8 High School

29:34.510 --> 29:36.830
and Chuncheng Xinpeng.

29:36.830 --> 29:38.290
The game is about to begin.

29:38.520 --> 29:40.040
We have just received news

29:39.560 --> 29:40.710
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

29:40.070 --> 29:41.000
that for this match,

29:40.740 --> 29:42.020
[Hongjing No. 8 High School vs.
Chuncheng Xinpeng]

29:41.000 --> 29:43.110
due to various reasons,
Hongjing No. 8 High School

29:43.110 --> 29:45.170
will only have 10 players available.

29:45.270 --> 29:47.540
Their courage is truly admirable.

29:47.650 --> 29:50.380
[Hongjing No. 8 High 0-0
Chuncheng Xinpeng]

29:47.880 --> 29:50.480
However, in their previous match
against Hengjiu,

29:50.480 --> 29:52.880
Hongjing No. 8 High School
suffered a heavy 11-0 defeat.

29:52.880 --> 29:55.440
With one player down this time, can they

29:55.440 --> 29:57.270
really turn things around

29:57.270 --> 29:58.640
and claim victory?

29:58.640 --> 30:00.030
Let's wait and see.

30:04.400 --> 30:06.260
-We've got this!
-We've got this!

30:10.160 --> 30:11.720
The match has now officially started,

30:11.720 --> 30:13.550
with Hongjing No. 8 High School
kicking off.

30:13.550 --> 30:14.680
-We can see that Hongjing No. 8 High School
-Here!

30:14.680 --> 30:16.680
has started the game on the front foot.

30:16.680 --> 30:18.590
The players are trying
to control the tempo

30:18.590 --> 30:20.960
through aggressive pressing
and challenges.

30:20.960 --> 30:21.720
It is a good idea,

30:21.720 --> 30:22.720
but reality is harsh.

30:22.720 --> 30:24.160
After all,
they are playing with one player short.

30:24.160 --> 30:25.590
-As expected, Xinpeng have taken control of the game
-I'll cover!

30:25.590 --> 30:27.320
and are piling on the pressure!

30:28.000 --> 30:29.400
Lin Lu wins the ball back.

30:37.310 --> 30:39.000
Xinpeng's No. 7 picks it up on the wing,

30:39.000 --> 30:40.350
beats the midfielder,

30:40.350 --> 30:41.590
gets past the defender,

30:41.590 --> 30:43.240
and drives into the box!

31:02.040 --> 31:03.120
[Hongjing to Chuncheng]

31:08.920 --> 31:10.070
There's a fire over there.

31:10.070 --> 31:11.350
Looks pretty bad.

31:11.350 --> 31:14.070
It'll probably take a while
for the traffic police to clear it.

31:14.070 --> 31:15.480
It's a national highway,
not an expressway.

31:15.480 --> 31:16.930
If traffic backs up,
it'll be at least an hour.

31:16.930 --> 31:19.400
[2:14 PM]

31:33.310 --> 31:34.040
Wen Chengye,

31:34.610 --> 31:36.940
it's okay that you're missing this match.

31:37.120 --> 31:38.920
There'll be other opportunities.

31:38.920 --> 31:40.240
I just want you to see

31:40.240 --> 31:41.480
how your teammates fight

31:41.480 --> 31:43.140
and never give up on the field.

31:46.270 --> 31:46.820
[Ms. Lin]

31:55.470 --> 32:00.250
[Wen Chengye]

31:56.000 --> 31:57.590
Ms. Lin, I'm on my way.

31:57.590 --> 31:58.790
There's been a little situation.

31:58.790 --> 31:59.480
Wait for me.

32:00.790 --> 32:03.030
Wen Chengye said he's on his way.

32:05.110 --> 32:05.840
Don't worry.

32:07.270 --> 32:09.730
They can hold out
until Wen Chengye arrives.

32:10.130 --> 32:15.660
[Wen Chengye]

32:10.480 --> 32:11.510
Be careful on the way.

32:11.510 --> 32:12.970
We are all waiting for you.

32:20.750 --> 32:22.720
Hongjing No. 8 High School
have fallen back into a defensive shape.

32:22.720 --> 32:25.270
Every player is in their own half.

32:25.270 --> 32:27.750
The disadvantage of playing
with one man down is very obvious.

32:27.750 --> 32:28.880
Come on, Zhi Hui, the middle!

32:28.880 --> 32:30.160
Xinpeng are now almost completely

32:30.160 --> 32:31.960
in control of the game.

32:31.960 --> 32:33.160
But Hongjing haven't given up.

32:33.160 --> 32:34.480
They're still pressing aggressively.

32:34.480 --> 32:35.350
Hopefully their stamina

32:35.350 --> 32:36.640
can last until the end.

32:36.640 --> 32:38.000
Xinpeng are passing the ball around,

32:38.000 --> 32:40.060
looking to break through the middle.

32:40.550 --> 32:41.830
Hongjing's No. 9, Qin Ao,

32:41.830 --> 32:43.030
makes a brilliant sliding tackle

32:43.030 --> 32:43.960
to clear the ball

32:43.960 --> 32:46.240
and stop a dangerous attack.

32:46.240 --> 32:47.510
The middle, Zhi Hui!

32:49.000 --> 32:49.880
Cover!

32:51.000 --> 32:51.660
Over there!

32:54.750 --> 32:56.150
Come on! Cover the right!

33:03.160 --> 33:03.790
Come on!

33:05.960 --> 33:07.790
Xinpeng win back possession once again.

33:07.790 --> 33:09.120
Qin Ao is tracking back.

33:18.830 --> 33:21.310
Hongjing make another
successful interception.

33:21.310 --> 33:22.200
Again!

33:22.590 --> 33:23.830
Even if I can't score,

33:23.830 --> 33:26.360
I won't let your defenders
get past midfield.

33:27.760 --> 33:28.560
No.

33:28.580 --> 33:30.010
I have to tell Ms. Lin.

33:34.110 --> 33:36.400
Oh no, Wen Chengye is stuck in traffic.

33:37.480 --> 33:39.340
Don't worry, there's still time.

33:42.000 --> 33:43.830
Xinpeng are making good use
of their numerical advantage,

33:43.830 --> 33:45.720
patiently moving the ball around
to stretch Hongjing's defense.

33:45.720 --> 33:47.550
Xinpeng keep building the attack.

33:47.550 --> 33:49.070
The ball reaches Xinpeng's No. 10.

33:49.070 --> 33:51.480
A Hongjing No. 8 High player
closes him down,

33:51.480 --> 33:53.750
trying to cut off his passing options.

33:53.750 --> 33:55.110
No. 10 plays it out wide!

33:55.110 --> 33:56.170
Cross into the box!

33:56.400 --> 33:58.530
The ball is sent into the penalty area,

34:05.160 --> 34:07.760
but Feng Suo gets a foot to it
and knocks it away!

34:49.920 --> 34:50.360
Today,

34:50.360 --> 34:52.000
Hongjing goalkeeper Feng Suo

34:52.000 --> 34:53.480
has been outstanding,

34:53.480 --> 34:55.590
making one save after another

34:55.590 --> 34:57.440
and keeping Hongjing's hopes

34:57.440 --> 34:59.170
alive.

34:59.800 --> 35:00.920
Left!

35:27.130 --> 35:28.110
We're now in the

35:28.110 --> 35:29.920
35th minute of the first half.

35:29.920 --> 35:31.510
The determined Hongjing No. 8 High School

35:31.510 --> 35:33.480
are still holding on,

35:33.480 --> 35:35.010
with the score level at 0-0.

35:56.670 --> 35:57.760
That's a foul!

35:57.760 --> 36:00.000
A Hongjing player
commits a foul with an accidental push.

36:00.000 --> 36:02.280
Fortunately,
it wasn't serious or intentional.

36:02.280 --> 36:04.000
The referee awards a direct free kick

36:04.000 --> 36:05.860
but keeps the cards in his pocket.

36:37.920 --> 36:39.710
Xinpeng's captain

36:39.710 --> 36:41.320
sends the ball into the box.

36:43.230 --> 36:45.000
No. 11 is trying to get on the end of it!

36:45.000 --> 36:46.440
A diving header!

36:48.110 --> 36:49.150
Goal!

36:49.590 --> 36:50.630
It's 1-0!

36:51.550 --> 36:52.880
Chuncheng Xinpeng

36:52.880 --> 36:54.670
have broken the deadlock.

36:55.070 --> 36:58.070
Even Feng Suo, who is in great form today,

36:58.070 --> 37:01.280
had no chance of stopping that one.

37:07.960 --> 37:09.670
Captain. Captain.

37:10.190 --> 37:11.390
1-0.

37:11.630 --> 37:13.490
You guys aren't that good.

37:15.480 --> 37:16.630
Good shot, brothers!

37:16.630 --> 37:17.320
Let's keep this up!

37:17.320 --> 37:17.800
Keep this up!

37:17.800 --> 37:19.030
Come on!

37:19.030 --> 37:20.000
-Let's continue!
-One more goal!

37:20.000 --> 37:20.800
One more!

37:22.960 --> 37:23.630
We are one man down.

37:23.630 --> 37:25.230
What is he so arrogant about?

37:25.550 --> 37:26.320
It's fine.

37:27.000 --> 37:28.230
Come on, everyone!

37:28.230 --> 37:28.830
Keep it up!

37:29.230 --> 37:30.030
No problem!

37:30.800 --> 37:32.360
It was actually a pass.

37:33.590 --> 37:34.630
What a pity.

37:34.880 --> 37:36.710
The first half is almost over.

37:37.110 --> 37:39.860
Zhou Siyan knew the risk
of shooting directly was high.

37:39.860 --> 37:40.990
From that position,

37:41.070 --> 37:42.740
no matter how much he curled the ball,

37:42.740 --> 37:44.340
it'd most likely be blocked.

37:47.360 --> 37:49.090
If Wen Chengye had been here...

37:49.610 --> 37:50.740
If he had been there,

37:51.030 --> 37:53.030
all he had to do was track back in time

37:53.280 --> 37:55.810
or put a little pressure
on the ball in the box,

37:56.710 --> 37:58.310
and it wouldn't have gone in.

38:17.280 --> 38:20.190
The ball landed right where
I was supposed to be defending.

38:20.190 --> 38:21.230
Damn it!

38:21.410 --> 38:23.540
[Think about what you've done!]

38:26.000 --> 38:27.860
We could've prevented that goal!

38:33.190 --> 38:36.180
[Dad]

38:39.660 --> 38:44.410
[Dad]

38:39.840 --> 38:41.320
Get your ass back here!

38:41.320 --> 38:43.230
Think about what you've done.

38:48.620 --> 38:57.620
[Lin Wanxing]

38:49.030 --> 38:50.010
Ms. Lin.

38:50.200 --> 38:51.150
Wait for me.

38:51.230 --> 38:52.030
I'll be there.

38:53.190 --> 38:54.380
Tell them

38:54.410 --> 38:55.740
to hold on.

38:56.230 --> 38:56.920
Wait for me.

39:00.630 --> 39:01.270
Sir!

39:03.190 --> 39:04.030
Sir, open the door.

39:04.030 --> 39:04.960
I need to get off!

39:26.440 --> 39:27.400
Nineteen.

39:27.710 --> 39:29.150
We blocked 19 shots.

39:30.830 --> 39:32.720
It was my fault
for setting up the defensive line.

39:32.720 --> 39:35.050
I really didn't expect them to cooperate.

39:37.030 --> 39:38.290
I was too slow to cover.

39:39.360 --> 39:39.880
No.

39:41.150 --> 39:43.000
It was my fault for not blocking the shot.

39:43.000 --> 39:44.230
It was my fault.

39:45.710 --> 39:47.960
Wen Chengye said he's coming.

39:49.480 --> 39:50.320
Wen Chengye?

39:51.190 --> 39:52.030
He's coming?

39:52.360 --> 39:53.620
Wen Chengye is coming?

39:55.820 --> 39:57.030
[WeChat]

39:57.030 --> 40:03.200
[Wen Chengye]

39:57.820 --> 39:59.310
I'm on my way to Chuncheng.

39:59.330 --> 40:00.650
No next time.

40:00.990 --> 40:02.360
I'm coming this time.

40:02.380 --> 40:03.700
We must win.

40:03.860 --> 40:04.930
Wen Chengye is really coming.

40:04.080 --> 40:05.780
[Youth Football Super League]

40:05.030 --> 40:05.890
He's on his way!

40:06.590 --> 40:07.670
My god.

40:07.670 --> 40:08.710
Is he crazy?

40:08.710 --> 40:10.160
It's already this late.

40:10.190 --> 40:10.840
What's the point?

40:10.840 --> 40:11.710
Yeah.

40:11.710 --> 40:13.510
What's the use of him coming now?

40:15.070 --> 40:16.400
Because he wants to win.

40:22.710 --> 40:23.590
I mean,

40:25.000 --> 40:26.030
we all want to win,

40:26.800 --> 40:27.710
don't we?

40:29.480 --> 40:30.000
Right.

40:31.150 --> 40:31.880
I want to win.

40:40.590 --> 40:41.520
I want to win too.

40:42.650 --> 40:44.360
Then let's play until we're satisfied.

40:44.360 --> 40:45.110
Let's do it!

41:05.880 --> 41:06.590
Come on, brothers!

41:06.590 --> 41:08.790
Let's score two more in the second half.

41:15.840 --> 41:16.670
Wen Chengye,

41:17.110 --> 41:19.310
you are not the only one who wants to win.

41:23.920 --> 41:25.520
The second half is underway.

41:29.960 --> 41:31.060
No. 6, Lin Lu,

41:31.510 --> 41:33.000
comes in too aggressively.

41:33.000 --> 41:34.440
He charges in from the side at full speed

41:34.440 --> 41:35.760
but can't stop his momentum

41:35.760 --> 41:37.320
-and crashes into the opponent, sending him to the ground.
-Hongjing's No. 6 commits a foul!

41:37.320 --> 41:38.710
-A charging foul!
-Yellow card warning.

41:38.710 --> 41:40.840
The referee makes the decision quickly
and shows Lin Lu a yellow card.

41:40.840 --> 41:43.480
Hongjing are really having
a tough time now.

41:43.480 --> 41:44.280
It's too hard.

41:44.590 --> 41:46.710
If Lin Lu picks up another yellow card,

41:46.710 --> 41:48.510
he'll be sent off,

41:48.510 --> 41:51.240
leaving Hongjing
with only 9 players against 11.

41:59.810 --> 42:01.740
[Microphone is on] [Speaker on]
[Camera off]

42:03.230 --> 42:04.070
Wen Chengye.

42:04.890 --> 42:06.080
I don't know

42:04.930 --> 42:07.470
[Microphone is on] [Speaker on]
[Camera off]

42:06.110 --> 42:07.370
if there's still time.

42:08.440 --> 42:09.760
But I'll still come.

42:10.800 --> 42:11.780
I definitely will.

42:11.780 --> 42:12.510
Wait for me.

42:13.630 --> 42:14.760
You must wait for me!

42:20.760 --> 42:22.220
We are all waiting for you.

42:26.070 --> 42:26.800
Hold on!

42:30.000 --> 42:32.150
The players on the field are exhausted.

42:32.150 --> 42:33.630
Especially for Hongjing No. 8 High School,

42:33.630 --> 42:34.960
who are playing with one man down,

42:34.960 --> 42:36.490
the test is even more cruel.

42:37.150 --> 42:38.960
Xinpeng's attack is very swift and fierce.

42:38.960 --> 42:40.510
-They are relentlessly attacking
-Nice ball!

42:40.510 --> 42:42.230
Hongjing No. 8 High School's defense.

42:42.230 --> 42:43.630
Can Hongjing hold on?

42:50.400 --> 42:51.550
Goalkeeper Feng Suo

42:51.550 --> 42:53.960
makes another key save!

42:53.960 --> 42:55.920
-He crashed into the pillar.
-Let's go!

42:55.920 --> 42:57.360
-But he held the ball tightly.
-Qin Ao!

42:57.360 --> 42:58.880
The ball is blocked!

42:59.820 --> 43:02.630
♪ Who hasn't known
the dark of night and uncertainty? ♪

43:00.230 --> 43:01.840
Hongjing finally gets a

43:01.840 --> 43:03.360
rare counterattack opportunity.

43:03.360 --> 43:05.960
No. 9 Qin Ao breaks through one-on-one,

43:03.670 --> 43:06.860
♪ Stumbling, covered in wounds,
losing direction ♪

43:05.960 --> 43:07.670
charging forward with everything he has!

43:07.670 --> 43:13.140
♪ Wandering alone,
gaining strength through pain ♪

43:15.960 --> 43:18.820
♪ Riding the wind,
chasing an unknown horizon ♪

43:20.030 --> 43:23.220
♪ Looking up,
dreaming side by side of great ideals ♪

43:24.120 --> 43:29.870
♪ The vast world
awaits youth to arrive ♪

43:30.800 --> 43:33.450
♪ If braving the wind
and waves ♪

43:34.550 --> 43:37.250
♪ What it takes to grow ♪

43:38.640 --> 43:40.870
♪ I will stubbornly
go against the current ♪

43:42.180 --> 43:44.490
♪ And let myself go wild ♪

43:45.890 --> 43:48.740
♪ No matter how long the road ahead ♪

43:50.110 --> 43:52.460
♪ Nothing can stop me ♪

43:54.140 --> 43:55.100
♪ Break through every haze of doubt ♪

43:54.800 --> 43:57.400
The match has reached the 87th minute.

43:56.130 --> 43:57.350
♪ Chase the light within me ♪

43:58.030 --> 44:00.840
Hongjing No. 8 High School
are still trailing 0-1,

43:58.630 --> 44:00.670
♪ Strong wings grow through the storm ♪

44:00.840 --> 44:02.260
but the players have never given up.

44:01.830 --> 44:04.640
♪ Even if no one cheers ♪

44:02.280 --> 44:04.630
-The Hongjing goalkeeper has once again
-Suo!

44:04.630 --> 44:05.710
pulled off several incredible saves

44:05.710 --> 44:06.550
and heroic defensive efforts!

44:05.790 --> 44:07.930
♪ I'll keep fighting my way through ♪

44:06.550 --> 44:08.230
Let's remember his name:

44:08.230 --> 44:08.960
Feng Suo!

44:09.400 --> 44:10.840
As long as I don't give up on scoring,

44:09.710 --> 44:11.270
♪ On a deserted battlefield ♪

44:10.840 --> 44:12.360
I can hold back the opponent's defender.

44:12.230 --> 44:13.370
♪ Thrive and bloom ♪

44:12.360 --> 44:13.630
I can't give up attacking!

44:13.630 --> 44:15.110
I absolutely cannot give up!

44:14.240 --> 44:17.180
♪ I'll take every scar ♪

44:18.100 --> 44:21.000
♪ As my badge of honor ♪

