Nice ball!

45:13.520 --> 45:15.450
♪ On a deserted battlefield ♪

45:13.630 --> 45:14.400
The 22nd.

45:16.000 --> 45:17.480
♪ Thrive and bloom ♪

45:17.990 --> 45:21.300
♪ I'll take every scar ♪

45:21.750 --> 45:25.480
♪ As my badge of honor ♪

45:26.060 --> 45:27.100
The 23rd.

45:39.320 --> 45:40.880
Xinpeng, unable to score for a long time,

45:40.880 --> 45:43.230
start to launch their fiercest attack.

45:43.230 --> 45:44.710
Playing with 10 men

45:44.710 --> 45:47.060
is a huge drain on Hongjing's stamina.

45:47.480 --> 45:48.440
Hold on!

45:55.320 --> 45:57.450
I'll save this shot even if it kills me!

46:40.550 --> 46:42.070
It's the last shot.

46:48.880 --> 46:49.840
The match is over.

46:49.840 --> 46:51.590
The final score is 0-1.

46:51.590 --> 46:54.070
Thanks to both sides
for bringing us a wonderful match,

46:54.070 --> 46:56.790
a magnificent 10-against-11 performance.

46:57.320 --> 46:59.480
Hongjing go down with honor.

46:59.480 --> 47:01.550
They have won everyone's respect.

47:01.550 --> 47:04.880
With running, sweat,
and even their bodies,

47:04.880 --> 47:06.920
they defended not only the goal

47:06.920 --> 47:08.960
but also their belief and dignity.

47:13.840 --> 47:15.150
We were so close!

47:44.110 --> 47:46.320
Coach asked us
which attack we wanted to stop.

47:46.320 --> 47:47.670
I know the answer now.

47:53.030 --> 47:53.800
This one,

47:54.440 --> 47:55.280
the next one,

47:55.480 --> 47:56.400
and every one.

47:57.190 --> 47:58.520
No matter which attack,

47:59.670 --> 48:01.030
we have to stop it.

48:44.920 --> 48:45.920
Wen Chengye?

48:53.590 --> 48:54.800
Wen Chengye is here.

49:03.840 --> 49:04.760
I'm sorry.

49:27.190 --> 49:29.030
I'm the one who should say sorry.

49:35.510 --> 49:36.710
I'm sorry, everyone.

49:41.000 --> 49:42.030
I'm sorry.

49:48.490 --> 49:50.260
I'm truly sorry.

50:02.920 --> 50:04.360
You once asked me

50:06.070 --> 50:07.670
what football is.

50:08.260 --> 50:10.190
I have thought about this question

50:10.630 --> 50:12.190
for a very long time,

50:13.630 --> 50:15.480
because I felt it was too hard.

50:19.710 --> 50:20.590
But now,

50:22.710 --> 50:24.710
I seem to finally have an answer.

50:27.670 --> 50:29.070
Football is competition

50:29.400 --> 50:30.530
and confrontation.

50:30.880 --> 50:32.960
It is the desire
to still stand on the pitch

50:32.960 --> 50:35.590
with your teammates
after countless disagreements.

50:33.230 --> 50:34.520
♪ Time's passing by ♪

50:35.170 --> 50:37.060
♪ Nothing remains ♪

50:36.920 --> 50:38.240
It is wanting to give up

50:38.150 --> 50:40.720
♪ All the dreamers awake alone ♪

50:38.700 --> 50:40.220
but being unable to,

50:40.360 --> 50:42.230
and finding the courage
to keep moving forward.

50:41.420 --> 50:43.120
♪ Shadows above ♪

50:43.010 --> 50:44.310
It is refusing

50:43.910 --> 50:45.620
♪ Rain falls around ♪

50:45.360 --> 50:46.500
to surrender to fate.

50:46.200 --> 50:47.030
♪ In your arms ♪

50:47.830 --> 50:49.300
♪ We become one ♪

50:50.080 --> 50:51.740
♪ Through day and night ♪

50:52.480 --> 50:54.510
♪ I can see you ♪

50:55.560 --> 50:57.800
♪ In my eyes ♪

50:58.660 --> 51:00.130
♪ Just hold me tight ♪

51:00.970 --> 51:06.180
♪ Look into my soul so deeply ♪

51:06.920 --> 51:08.670
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

51:09.520 --> 51:10.660
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

51:11.570 --> 51:12.150
♪ Wonderful days ♪
